snippet.title: Starlight Legacy - Demo Version Trailer
snippet.description:
Forge your own legacy in Starlight Legacy! Explore the vast Evaria Kingdom in beautiful 2D pixel art graphics, an exciting turn-based battle system, and a non-linear story.
A playable demo is coming soon to Steam and itch.io!

Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/2696760/Starlight_Legacy/
